snippet.title: Tombwater | Official Announcement
snippet.description:
Wishlist Tombwater on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3308200/Tombwater/

A Souls-Like Western coming to PC in 2025. Explore the accursed Wild West town of Tombwater and lay bare the eldritch horrors that lie within. Survive blood-spilling combat in this gruesome 2D action-RPG that might just drive you to madness.

STUDIO:  Moth Atlas
DISCORD: https://bit.ly/3HwLoDF
